data.description: Welcome to this charming duplex nestled in the heart of South Philadelphia. This classic property has been thoughtfully updated to blend its historic charm with modern amenities. Ideal for both investors and owner-occupants looking for a comfortable home with rental income potential. This move-in-ready duplex also opens doors to a profitable Airbnb venture. Take advantage of the bustling tourism scene in Philadelphia by hosting travelers in this well-appointed property. Your future guests will appreciate the convenience and comfort this duplex provides. 1623 is located in the lovely Girard Estate Area, allowing individuals to immerse themselves in the vibrant culture and lifestyle that Philadelphia has to offer. Making it an attractive choice for those seeking an urban living experience with easy access to the city's amenities and attractions. Each unit offers open floor plans, separate utilities, and spacious living areas, adding to the allure of 1623. Arrange your showing to experience the unique charm and potential of this duplex firsthand!
